   554â†’                <p>Eze's delivery was nothing short of brilliantâ€”a curling rocket that soared past Chelsea goalkeeper Robert Sanchez and into the top corner. Palace fans erupted, and it seemed like a pivotal moment in the game. However, celebrations were cut short as referee Darren England was called to the pitchside monitor by VAR officials.</p>
