   582â†’                        <li><strong>Infringement Detection:</strong> Guehi was within the restricted zone and pushed Caicedo, violating the rule</li>
   583â†’                        <li><strong>Consequence:</strong> The free-kick is retaken, and the goal is nullified if scored</li>
   584â†’                    </ol>
   585â†’                </div>
   586â†’                
   587â†’                <p>This "little-known rule" has caught many off guard, but it's designed to prevent jostling and promote fair play. Searches for "Marc Guehi encroachment Eze free kick" highlight how this specific violation was the deciding factor, not offside or handball as some initially assumed.</p>
